Soxy, your favourite proxy
==========================

Soxy is a proxy that transparently provides a proxy for any kind of application.
Under the hood it uses system call interception (with ptrace) to transparently
redirect any traffic to the proxy server.

Features:
    -   IPv4 / IPv6.
    -   TCP & UDP.
    -   Rule-based forwarding.
    -   Track all process children.

Future work:
    -   VPN variant of soxy. (ptrace-based vpn)
